A skyhook is a thing which gives leaving rockets from earth force of momentum and speeds them of to interstellar space.
So to build it we'll need a strong cable, a giant counterweight and a hook.
And for launching it.we'll need a rocket with a cannon which shoots the skyhook like a net.





So the disscussion about the skyhook is,  how to lauch the skyhook in a more convinient way. Leave your suggestions in comments section.

